# atlas append shard — sim Stage-5 scale-up sweep
# Module: nexus/sim_bridge/anu_time/scale_universe.hexa (read-only)
# Probe: σ² ∈ {64, 512, 1024, 4096} at ticks ∈ {4, 8}
# ★ Energy is SUB-EXTENSIVE (E ∝ cells^0.55, not ∝ cells)
# ★ Energy density decreases 6.3× from σ²=64 to σ²=4096
