  → "raw 91 C3 strict — Stage-5 scale-up findings:"
  → "  Read-only: zero modifications to scale_universe.hexa or any source"
  → "  Probes: 6 background runs + 1 selftest + 1 benchmark + 2 single-σ²"
  → "  Successful data points: 8 (σ²×ticks combos, all 3 reruns idempotent)"
